%matplotlib inline
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np

x = np.linspace(0, 10, 100)
y = np.cos(x)

plt.plot(x, y)
plt.xlabel('x')
plt.ylabel('y')
plt.title('Simple Plot')
plt.grid(True)
plt.show()
